Install Terraform: 
1. https://hashicorp-terraform.awsworkshop.io/030_self_guided_setup/37_install_terraform_cli.html
2. https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/tutorials/aws-get-started/aws-build

Install aws cli:
1. sudo apt install unzip
2. curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"
unzip awscliv2.zip
3. sudo ./aws/install

Verify the installation : /usr/local/bin/aws --version
Configure the aws : aws configure
                    Enter your Access key and security credentials from aws


Reference: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs
